Package: learnstats
Type: Package
Title: An Interactive Environment for Learning Statistics
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2016-02-25
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Walter", email = "dswalter@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows students with limited programming
    experience to use R as an interactive educational environment
    for statistical concepts, ranging from p-values to confidence intervals
    to stability in time series.
License: GPL
LazyData: TRUE
